primary.context: Caller needed instructions on how to complete or submit their rental agreement
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller and sent a link to complete the rental agreement online.

steps: Caller asked for instructions on rental agreement
Agent performed account lookup via phone number
Agent verified caller name and state
Agent explained the purpose of the rental agreement
Agent offered and sent a link to the caller's email and phone
Caller confirmed no further needs and call ended

clarifications.note: Agent proactively asked for name spelling for verification

actions.detail: Verified name spelling and state of Indiana
Sent rental agreement link to email and phone

insights.summary: The caller wanted to know how to handle their rental agreement; the agent verified their identity and sent a digital link to complete it.
insights.verbatim: What do I do with the rental agreement?
